name: Untitled Cat Project
description:
Game Overview:

Untitled Cat Project is a third-person game where the player controls a humanoid kitty to jump around and up in a 3D space by holding the space key, and complete the level by successfully acquiring the tuna can on top.

Goal: Use charged jump and items collected on the way up strategically to get to the top of the level and get the missing tuna can back.

Creators:

Evelyn You(Game/UI Design)

Siddharth Vimala Ravindren(Game Design/3D Art)

Luke Qian(Game/Level Design)

P.B.Giridharahn(Game Developer)

Cool Gavin(Game Developer)
